OL,5, Troubled crypto firm FTX collapsed     
OL,6, after being "run as a personal fiefdom 
OL,7, of Sam Bankman-Fried", a US bankruptcy 
OL,8, court has heard.                       
OL,10,FThe former FTX boss led the firm once  
OL,11,Fvalued at $40bn (#33.7bn), but lacked  
OL,12,Fbasic money controls, a lawyer leading 
OL,13,Fthe bankruptcy proceedings said.       
OL,15,FThe true state of FTX's finances was   
OL,16,Fonly now being understood, he said.    
OL,18,FHe also claimed Mr Bankman-Fried's team
OL,19,Fspent roughly $300m on holiday homes   
OL,20,Fand property for senior staff.         
